  - Independent auditor se multi-seat mandate aur leadership eligibility verify karein
  - Six-seat caucus ka ethics, dissent and conflict charter publish karein
  - Five priority areas ka costed fictional shadow budget publish karein
  - Seven public groups ke equal-time regional hearings complete karein
  - Shanti ke saath women-youth policy leadership council train karein
  - Samrat ke saath neutral emergency and crowd-safety coordination review karein
  - Open caucus ballot ya closed loyalty deal mein leadership decision lein
  - Evidence-led legislative research and correction workflow activate karein
  - Fictional leadership rumour ko source-backed correction se answer karein
  - Evidence-led state policy convention and dissent session complete karein
  - Assets, endorsements, conflicts and caucus vote ka final ethics audit close karein
  - Independent panel par computed state-leadership selection dekhein
